STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Cross-Petitioner,
v.
Amy LOCANE a/k/a Amy Bovenizer, and Amy Locane-Bovenizer, Defendant-Cross-Respondent. C-213 September Term 2018
081057 Supreme Court of New Jersey. OCTOBER 24, 2018

ORDER

A cross-petition for certification of the judgment in A-001990-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the cross-petition for certification is denied.
